open terminal
# run ./imroot firstly, only once is enough
run ./startup.sh, wait for line as "x7_manage/server/mq_receiver.py"
start browser with url 127.0.0.1:8000/init
set correct value, especially interface, like "eth0"

click submit and have a look at the terminal for the output. 
It will install everything that server need.
You will see msg like "stack.sh completed in $SECONDS seconds." when success

